            "title": "Chemical Composition of the Substances from Dorsal Patches of Males of the CuraÇAoan Long-Nosed Bat, Leptonycteris curasoae (Phyllostomidae: Glossophaginae)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Mariana",
