            "title": "Genetic Analyses Reveal High Connectivity among Populations of the Honduran White Bat Ectophylla alba in the Caribbean Lowlands of Central Eastern Costa Rica",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Edgar G.",
                    "lastName": "Gutiérrez"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
